## \uc0\u55356 \u57263  What is Mosaic Magazine HI?\
\
Mosaic Magazine HI is a comprehensive online magazine platform designed specifically for K-12 students and teachers in NYC schools. It empowers students to publish their creative work\'97stories, poetry, artwork, photography, and more\'97in a professional digital magazine format that celebrates student voice and creativity.\
\
Think of it as a combination of:\
- **A student newspaper** (but digital and more engaging)\
- **A creative portfolio platform** (where students showcase their best work)\
- **A collaborative publishing studio** (where teachers and editors work together to publish student content)\
