## \uc0\u10024  Core Features & Capabilities\
\
### 1. Content Submission System\
\
**What It Does:**\
Students and teachers can submit their creative work through an easy-to-use form.\
\
**How It Works:**\
1. User logs in with their email\
2. Fills out a submission form with:\
   - Title and description\
   - Author name and grade level\
   - Content type (poem, story, artwork, photo, etc.)\
   - Upload files (images, PDFs, documents)\
3. Submits for review\
4. Receives notifications about submission status\
\
**Key Benefits:**\
- \uc0\u9989  Simple file upload with automatic validation\
- \uc0\u9989  Support for multiple content types\
- \uc0\u9989  Students can track their submissions\
- \uc0\u9989  Automatic organization and categorization\
- \uc0\u9989  File size limits prevent server overload (images: 10MB, PDFs: 25MB)\
\
